```javascript
// ry-ui.js中代码：
selectUserName: function(datas, value) {
    var actions = [];
    $.each(datas,
    function(index, user) {
        if (user.userId == ('' + value)) {
            actions.push($.common.sprintf("<span  class='%s'>%s</span>", "", user.userName));
            return false;
        }
    });
    return actions.join('');
},
```

